Class PluginSelector

java.lang.Object
java.awt.Component
java.awt.Container
java.awt.Window
java.awt.Dialog
javax.swing.JDialog
org.graffiti.managers.pluginmgr.PluginSelector
All Implemented Interfaces:
ActionListener, MouseListener, WindowListener, ImageObserver, MenuContainer, Serializable, EventListener, Accessible, ListSelectionListener, RootPaneContainer, WindowConstants
public class PluginSelector
extends JDialog
implements ActionListener, MouseListener, ListSelectionListener, WindowListener
Represents a plugin selector. A simple dialog to pick the name of a plugin. The dialog filters already loaded plugins from the list of plugins.
Version:
$Revision: 1.8 $
